'''国际和平局（IPB：International Peace Bureau)''' 成立于1891年<ref name="IPB history">{{cite web |url=http://ipb.org/i/about-ipb/II-B-01-history-century-of-peace-making.html |title=Over a Century of Peace-Making |publisher=International Peace Bureau |access-date=2012-02-14 |dead-url=yes |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130415051815/http://ipb.org/i/about-ipb/II-B-01-history-century-of-peace-making.html |archive-date=2013-04-15 }}</ref>，是世界上最早成立的国际和平组织，1910年获得[[诺贝尔和平奖|诺贝尔和平奖]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Award Ceremony Speech (1910)|url=https://www.nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/peace/laureates/1910/press.html|access-date=2011-10-06|publisher=Nobel Foundation|archive-date=2011-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111006050340/http://www.nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/peace/laureates/1910/press.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=The Nobel Peace Prize 1910|url=http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/peace/laureates/1910/index.html|access-date=2011-10-06|publisher=Nobel Foundation|archive-date=2017-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171007170731/https://www.nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/peace/laureates/1910/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1913年，[[亨利·拉方丹|亨利·拉方丹]]也以国际和平局局長的身份获得[[诺贝尔和平奖|诺贝尔和平奖]]<ref name="Lundestad">{{cite web|last=Lundestad|first=Geir|author-link=Geir Lundestad|date=2001-03-15|title=The Nobel Peace Prize, 1901–2000|url=http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/peace/articles/lundestad-review/index.html|access-date=2011-10-06|publisher=Nobel Foundation|archive-date=2013-05-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130530223616/http://www.nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/peace/articles/lundestad-review/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=The Nobel Peace Prize 1913|url=http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/peace/laureates/1913/index.html|access-date=2011-10-06|publisher=Nobel Foundation|archive-date=2018-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180119120538/https://www.nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/peace/laureates/1913/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。截至2012年，共有12名国际和平局成员獲得诺贝尔和平奖<ref>{{cite web|title=IPB Nobel Prize Winners|url=http://ipb.org/i/about-ipb/II-B-03-history-laureates-and-leaders.html|dead-url=yes|archive-url=https://archive.is/20120718043929/http://ipb.org/i/about-ipb/II-B-03-history-laureates-and-leaders.html|archive-date=2012-07-18|access-date=2011-10-06|publisher=Nobel Foundation}}.</ref> 。

